<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Home Page</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f3ebf5;
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #5b4e77;
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #5b4e77;
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        p {
            color: #5b4e77;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .buttons {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .button {
            background-color: #5b4e77;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 200px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #473a5d;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Wellcome</h1>
    <h2>2025</h2>
    <p>you Don't Find Happy Life, you Make it</p>

    <div class="buttons">
        <a href="/todo" class="button">My Goals</a>
        <a href="/index" class="button">My Vision Board</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
